Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.14,0:00:05.90,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please can you keep my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:23.38,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror, shining so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:29.22,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how do I look in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:33.64,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The future, beckoning me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:38.52,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen from now, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:49.78,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because what we see is not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:52.61,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing myself but that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.20,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now try not to waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:00.16,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be true to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.92,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But even I have a secret or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:10.46,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That I want to keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:16.22,OP Style 2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my secret makes my heart aches slightly.
