Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:27.95,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,673)}We'll surely meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:41.42,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,90)}Everything that's reflected by your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.80,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,90)}is it all just an illusion?
