Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:13.29,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,90)}Isn't it fine just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:19.50,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,90)}It'll be an unadorned beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:23.88,TLK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,90)}Let's understand this, someday...
