Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outdoor education begins tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A relaxing 5 days and 4 nights to have fun in the wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can forget about studies, play tennis, and frolic in the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll engorge ourselves on nature's delights in the evening and then bathe in the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab and sell a few rhino beetles, and we'll have enough to indulge in Maid Latte for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from a senior that there's a dress-wearing beauty recovering in nearby villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is outdoor education that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! According to the seniors, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not listening to us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go back to our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're from a different class, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat bread crusts while walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely different from what we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are we training like this? Why are we in a temple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the seniors say that Seika's outdoor education is a paradise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is this dress-wearing beauty who's resting in a nearby villa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No normal person would reside in a mountain like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about stories the seniors told us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Seika Seniors traditionally deceive the 2nd years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deceive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure when it started, but the outdoor education bored the seniors to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they took it out on the juniors by lying to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outdoor education? It was fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you look a little worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun I lost weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should look forward to it next year! It's fantastic! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the deceived juniors did the same to their juniors, and it became an endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is just horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our hopes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are completely crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a time for learning! We're not here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your asses to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally appeared, that sensational transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking cheerful today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to confess again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not free period now. Get back to your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold, Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like I'm losing my edge nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prez, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just cleaning up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lying! He's dragging me around everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll handle that pervert myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take my eyes off of you for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just sulking a bit due to jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no reason to skip your tasks and make fun of Yukimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I think it is, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, why does he always end up leading the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fast at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm beat from all the preachings and cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we're lucky that we're preparing dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys still have to meditate under the waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wash the rice if you're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please gather the vegetable waste over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki's really amazing! She can take command so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of washing the tableware beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we never noticed how dirty they were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something that the Manager always does, but I can't tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, what about Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was curious about it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura's main objective right now is to talk about your love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect opportunity, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hinata appeared at just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's really curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with all of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing between us! We're just childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there more to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough time for anything like that anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got things to do as the Seika's Student Council President!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch over him like I did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hurts! What a hellish exercise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that guy's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really wild, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, he's a kid at heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that berry you just ate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really naive, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing to Usui-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, you're really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some awesome pecs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda dangerous, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was a girl, I would probably fall for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that so carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're speaking of {\i1}this{\i0} Usui, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might hit on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's that yummy looking red berry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be done here, from meditation to your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personal conversation is not normally allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, just for tonight, I won't mind a little bit of chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only having a small bowl of curry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was meat, but it's just konjac!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konjac curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no second helpings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! That wasn't enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should slowly enjoy the blessings nature bestowed upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not enough for me to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best to endure even though I was so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that idiot doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was told to sweep the grounds outside tonight as punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was merciless! This is scarier than the game of testing your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, since it's Hinata, I'm sure he'll wander off looking for food instead of sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like eating the food offered at graves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible! You never know what he'll do when he's alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so worrisome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that idiot go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find a flashlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to search for food in the mountain if I could find a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you enter the storeroom without asking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just wanted to borrow a flashli-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get out of there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get discovered by the monks-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, why is the storeroom door ajar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anyone in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, someone must've forgotten to lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doors won't bulge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be another way out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I hide just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'd listen to us if I told the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the heart-throbbing situation of two people in a locked room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I read about these in some mangas before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get some food! And then keep our bodies warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel cold, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have cellphones here... No reception, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What reception?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?! Embrace each other in the nude until morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally clueless about that-!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of mangas have you been reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your heart racing as well?! We're alone, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we have to hurry and find a way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both 16 year old teenagers of opposite genders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin...tani...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you do not think of me that way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to think of me as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! My face feels so hot! Am I'm blushing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me like that! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me to look, and then tell me to not look...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I want you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...think of you as a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll think of you as a man, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys completed the third day of outdoor education.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last night, we'll be camping outside of the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, be sure to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys are too tired to rampage around after three days of strict training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from a senior...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Danger will befall the girls on the fourth day," or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself, Usui Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys lately?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys fighting any time you meet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a passionate dialogue between men, right, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mr. Third Rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my name! I'm Shintani Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that your name? You're a third-rate man, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you're Mr. First Rate, in being annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and reflect on your actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why are they being pointlessly energetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as being pointlessly energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It's a wonderful thing to live your life to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only enjoy life if you're in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were too busy with our lives, and ended up forgetting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How inexperienced we are, to realize this only after experiencing the extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are grateful to be alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the guys, even the three idiots, have reached enlightenment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get stung everywhere at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get so inflamed that I'll look like another person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright? There's a lot of mosquitoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy to be popular, Mr. Third Rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among mosquitoes, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the Third Rate thing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get scolded by Prez if you make a fuss again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Do you... like Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, are you guys dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be this troubled if we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must it rain today of all days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was looking forward to camping outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys look like a bunch of zombies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, with them like that, we won't need to be worried 'bout what the seniors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again, "Danger will befall the girls on the fourth day"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tennis court!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get in right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having BBQ  at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, some meat after so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vegetarian meals didn't taste like actual food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were dead hungry from all the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,694)}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,694)}Is this paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,694)}This isn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?! Get back to your line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get any closer to the girls-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly like what the seniors said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, with the meditations, classes, and cleaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the insufficient food and sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all this dissatisfaction, they lose all rationality and go wild on the fourth day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They start attacking the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've never paid any attention to us before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any girl is fine at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those scum bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, hurry! Take refuge in the cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys snapped earlier than expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen them act this way before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason girls have less work the first three days
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to prepare for this day, or so I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this has happened before, eh...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.42,0:15:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, the teachers create a firm barricade that separates the boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the barricade, the girls have been fine so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long we don't get close to them-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The river bank near the camp collapsed from the heavy rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers can't create the barricade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, do you have any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be food prepared for tonight's BBQ, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Shall we help ourselves first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys gonna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main problem here is not our empty stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time we spent at the temple was strangely peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the girls must be free now since we are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they must feel insecure in this heavy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? We can't just leave them like that, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I just felt a shiver down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, are you really going out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the president, I need to do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what 'bout the guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! If the guys come here, stop them at all cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really came, eh? You worthless boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wanted to go see the girls, and I wanted to see you as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun to play poker with the girls under the teachers' noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintani...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think these guys just want to play poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as sharp as ever, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who gets rough with my Misaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you calling your Misaki-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the situation, will ya? These guys are crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll definitely upset the girls if they go there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only want to have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Playing tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be "it" then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch you if you don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Usui-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be "it" too, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we... play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not play now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play with non-violent rules, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't we chasing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! The whole purpose was to drive them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a victory for the "it"s, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! A total victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They changed their attitudes when Takumi appeared, for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the guys acknowledge Usui's superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's also what I felt from this outdoor education experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one amazing guy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, you're just amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your vocabulary's limited, isn't it, Mr. Third Rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! And don't use difficult words! {Difficult referring to 'vocabulary' I guess, since to Japanese, foreign words are hard}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant "You're an idiot!", Mr. Third Rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been devoured already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did this happen-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bread crust!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy, he already-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The BBQ will be done separately.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain's slowed down now, and the teachers are quickly creating the barricade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe for the girls to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some remark you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The two of them are getting along well even though they keep fighting"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be what you were thinking just now. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still thinking about that? Didn't I tell you to not worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you said the same thing to him as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that guy special to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "special"? There's nothing-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were childhood friends, so I've spent more time with him than other guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you were so worried you couldn't take your eyes off him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... You're always watching him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!  He's a troublesome idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... You're even more troublesome than him, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've pointlessly exhausted myself because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, it's about time for the guys' BBQ! You should hurry back if you're hungry-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the energy to move even an inch right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky cleared up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Shintani, devouring all the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a delicious lamb right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he were a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The training sure was tough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be thankful for the meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm grateful for the warm rays of sunlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enlightenment of the three idiots somehow seemed depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll be the first ones to deceive the second years next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, after having food from the wild, how about having something starting with "S"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi? Steak? Watermelon? Sukiyaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All wrong~! When it comes to food starting with "S", it has to be sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be an event related to sweets at Maid Latte...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.54,0:24:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Full-Course Sweets Challenge, Misa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell something sweet!
